## л°ҳліөлҗҳлҠ” н…ҢмҠӨнҠё м„Өм • л¶„лҰ¬н•ҳкё°

BeforeEachмҷҖ AfterEachлҠ” мҶҢмҶҚлҗң container node лӮҙмқҳ лӘЁл“  subject nodeк°Җ мӢӨн–үлҗҳкё° м „/нӣ„м—җ мӢӨн–үлҗ©лӢҲлӢӨ.

`go
var _ Describe("...", func () {
 var sharedVar Type

 BeforeEach(func () {
 // setup code for sharedVar
 })

 AfterEach(func () {
 // teardown code for sharedVar
 })

 It("...", func () {
 // test code using sharedVar
 })

 It("...", func () {
 // test code using sharedVar
 })
})
`

мң„ мҪ”л“ңлҠ” BeforeEach -\> It -\> AfterEach мҲңмңјлЎң мӢӨн–үлҗ©лӢҲлӢӨ.

`go
var _ = Describe("...", func () {
 var sharedVar sharedType

 BeforeEach(func () {
 // setup code for sharedVar
 })

 AfterEach(func () {
 // teardown code for sharedVar
 })

 Context("...", func () {
 It("...", func () {
 // test code using sharedVar
 })

 It("...", func () {
 // test code using sharedVar
 })
 })

 Context("...", func () {
 BeforeEach(func () {
 // additional setup code for this context
 })

 AfterEach(func () {
 // additional teardown code for this context
 })

 It("...", func () {
 // test code using sharedVar
 })

 It("...", func () {
 // test code using sharedVar
 })
 })
})
`

мң„ мҪ”л“ңмқҳ л‘җ лІҲм§ё subjectк°Җ мӢӨн–үлҗ  л•ҢлҠ” BeforeEach -\> Contextмқҳ BeforeEach -\> It -\> Contextмқҳ AfterEach -\> AfterEach мҲңмңјлЎң мӢӨн–үлҗ©лӢҲлӢӨ.

BeforeEachмҷҖ It мӮ¬мқҙм—җ мӢӨн–үлҗҳлҠ” JustBeforeEachлқјлҠ” кІғлҸ„ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ. л§Ҳм°¬к°Җм§ҖлЎң Itкіј AfterEach мӮ¬мқҙм—җ мӢӨн–үлҗҳлҠ” JustAfterEach`лҸ„ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.

